{
  "texts": [
    "For Sidi Bel Abbés station, the FSRA algorithm removes 46 unneeded IMFs elements from the entire dataset while maintaining the forecasting effectiveness of the IF-VMD-CNN model.",
    "The FSRA technique at Ghardaia station removes 84 redundant IMFs elements from the entire dataset while retaining the forecasting ability of the proposed IF-VMD-CNN model.",
    "The FSRA algorithm was useful in reducing the amount of IMFs elements for training our model while preserving forecasting effectiveness.",
    "This reveals the findings that FS techniques can improve the accuracy of PV power forecasting methods.",
    "It is concluded that using a feature selection technique in training the suggested methodology improves forecasting accuracy and computation efficiency."
  ]
}